_Blend Spaces_ are regular assets and must be created through the **Content Browser** like any other asset.

**To create a new _Blend Space_:**

1. In the **Content Browser**, navigate to the folder within which you want to create your new _Blend Space_, then click ![](Shared/EditorButtons/button_NewAsset.png) or **right-click** and choose **Animation** > **Blend Space**:

	![](NewBlendSpace.png)

1. In the **Choose Skeleton** dialog, select the Skeleton the _Blend Space_ should target:

	![](SkeletonList.png)

1. The new _Blend Space_ asset is displayed in the **Content Browser** at the location specified:

	![Create Blueprint - Asset Created](bs_create_asset.png)

	The _Blend Space_ is also available to be used in the **Anim Graphs** of _Animation Blueprints_ targeting the same Skeleton as the _Blend Space_:

	[REGION:imagetable]
	| ![](AssetBrowserBlendList.png)(h:400) | ![](ContextMenuBlendList.png)(h:400) |
	| :---: | :---: |
	| **Asset Browser** | **Context Menu** |
	[/REGION]

